  <p class="gd-byline" style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:12.5px;letter-spacing:.05em;color:var(--blue-soft);opacity:.9;margin:16px 0 0">By <a href="/about" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px">Vegard Knudsen</a> · Founder, Heliski Travel · Updated 25 May 2026</p>
  <p class="gd-lede">Japan holds the finest powder on Earth, yet <strong>dedicated heliskiing</strong> there is famously limited. This honest guide covers the snow, the terrain and the reality of flying, then points those wanting a full heli week toward our <a href="/packages">packages</a> and <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
